text: Everyone who has ever forgotten someone's name immediately after being introduced.
Everyone who has accidentally 'liked' a very old social media post while stalking.
Everyone who has said 'you too' to a waiter who said 'enjoy your meal'.
Everyone who has mistaken a stranger for someone they know.
Everyone who has had food stuck in their teeth without realizing it for hours.
Everyone who has replied to an email meant for 'reply all' with something embarrassing.
Everyone who has walked around with their zipper down.
Everyone who has tried to be cool and failed spectacularly.
Everyone who has told a joke that nobody laughed at.
Everyone who has started a story and then realized it wasn't appropriate for the audience.
